ound":true,"entry_ids":["n10277","n10298"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%AE%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10277","headword_ar":"اخرجّ","root":"xrj","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a ram, K, or an ostrich, S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoraj","text_ar":"اَخْرَج"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of two colours, white and black;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AxrAj~","text_ar":"اخراجّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n10298","headword_ar":"اَخْرَجُ","root":"xrj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A ram, (S, K,) and (so in the S, but in the K “ or ”) a male ostrich, (AA, S, A, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of two colours, white and black:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, * K:) or a male ostrich"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a colour in which black predominates over white, like the colour of ashes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in this sense also applied to a mountain: (Lth, TA:) and a goat"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"half white and half black:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and a horse"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which the belly, and the sides as far as the back, but not the back itself, are white, and the rest of any colour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarojaA='u","text_ar":"خَرْجَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A, TA:) which is applied to a female ostrich: (A:) and to a ewe or she-goat"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having white hind legs and flanks:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S:) or a ewe"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is black, with one hind leg,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"both hind legs, and the flanks, white; the rest being black:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or a ewe"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white in the hinder part, half of her being white, and the other half of any colour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA:) and a small isolated mountain ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaArapN","text_ar":"قَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of two colours,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white and black:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurojN","text_ar":"خُرْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) Also (tropical:)  A garment"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white and red;"},{"kind":"text","text":"rendered so by being besmeared with blood. (TA.) El-'Ajjáj says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"A_in~aA A_i*aA mu*okiY AlHuruwbi A^ar~ajaA\n                      \n                     \n                        walabisato lilomawoti vawobFA A^axorajaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so in the TA: in the S,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jul~FA AxrjA","text_ar":"جُلًّا اخرجا"},{"kind":"text","text":":) meaning (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily we, when the inflamer of wars excites"},{"kind":"text","text":"them,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the wars)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have put on, for death, a garment white and red, rendered so by being besmeared with blood:"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e., have been rendered notable like a thing that is black and white. (S, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^axoraju","text_ar":"الاَخْرَجُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bird called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muk~aA='","text_ar":"مُكَّا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) because of its colour. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN xarojaA='u","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ خَرْجَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxar~ajapN","text_ar":"مُخَرَّجَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhaA taxoriyjN","text_ar":"فِيهَا تَخْرِيجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Land having plants,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage, in one place and not in another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has been rained upon, and has produced herbs, in some parts and not in others:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh:) or the second means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land upon which rain has not fallen."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SH","text_ar":"صح"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmN A^axoraju","text_ar":"عَامٌ اَخْرَجُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxar~ajN","text_ar":"مُخَرَّجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi taxoriyjN","text_ar":"فِيهِ تَخْرِيجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw taxoriyjK","text_ar":"ذُو تَخْرِيجٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A year of fruitfulness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of abundant herbage, and of sterility:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"half fruitful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundant in herbage, and half sterile."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","AA","A","Lth","TA","AZ","T","Sh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}